Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:52.16,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,All the pirates vying for the One Piece\Nhead for the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:54.69,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,People call it the "New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.08,0:03:03.43,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,However, the only one to ever conquer\Nthese waters was the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:09.74,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.11,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Now, the boy whose body turned to rubber\Nafter eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.11,0:03:19.38,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nventure into that very sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.09,0:03:23.52,Default,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and his crew reached Fishman
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Island located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,where the New Fishman Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,who are looking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...assisted by Vander Decken,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,who is after Shirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats find themselves caught up in the turmoil and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Noah is already...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.65,0:03:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sea Kings? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama! The wound is opening up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.79,0:04:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You are bleeding a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Well... That's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...as long as the ship is stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"To the Future! The Path to the Sun!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Shirahoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We have been waiting for you to be born for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This ship is designed to be pulled by us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:05:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Since very early times, the duty has been passed on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why the Noah is so big?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Once in many centuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,our queen comes into the world in the form of Mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since you were born,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you have been our queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think Shirahoshi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.29,0:05:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She is talking with the Sea Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on, guards? How did the Noah stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.10,0:05:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, actually a group of Sea Kings showed up here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,around the island, out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed like they came to protect the Noah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:06:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...from getting destroyed by Luffy-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the Noah is something very important to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Neptune-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sea Kings...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It awakes finally-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The power that could destroy the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Look,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the bubble is getting absorbed by the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The human can't survive in the deep sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You better go and save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama! Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We should go capture Hody and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.56,0:06:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Noah... I wonder what secrets that ship holds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I imagining things?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That human with the hat noticed our voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Something like this happened not so long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rayleigh, did you just hear that voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.83,0:07:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really quiet down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you, talking in such deep sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,--I wonder why. --I wonder why as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Straw Hat and the others are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They're strong, aren't they? Then they're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, we have to trust them, Hatchin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.28,0:08:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sea Kings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.49,0:08:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They're pulling the Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna eat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship is falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it be fixed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it still work?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.57,0:08:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to fix it, we need help from "them" but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...times are changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it be fixed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it can be fixed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:08:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...by the appointed time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.93,0:09:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Ryugu Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Minister of the Left, you might want to hear this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.54,0:09:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.47,0:09:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We found the Mermaids who had been kidnapped...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.34,0:09:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...inside the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, they are. They say they still feel groggy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.55,0:09:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but they remember the kidnapper's face clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the treasure chamber's been emptied.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.46,0:09:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't even a single piece of treasure left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention the national treasure--the Tamate Box!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,King-sama! S-Somebody robbed the palace while we were gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.47,0:09:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about the treasure thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.64,0:09:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We almost lost the whole country just now-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, let the whole nation know that those Mermaids were okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's too late
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but we need to clear Straw Hat and the others' name-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We did them wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.53,0:10:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll catch and kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! We humans have nothing to do with this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's fly over him with bubbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Water Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I will shoot you down if you try to fly over me with those!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you, Boss! Let us go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just afraid of Hody and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We have nothing to do with this civil war because we're humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought this island was a tourist spot
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,largely depending on us human pirates for money!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us get out through the exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No one says that you all are going to get your heads cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for Neptune royal family's decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something that we would like all islanders to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats were not involved in the kidnap of the Mermaids at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We admit that we made a mistake in our fact-checking process
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and we take full responsibility - we want to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.61,0:11:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think the Straw Hats did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.15,0:11:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it wasn't them the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We all thought that they were the kidnappers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,--N-No, we trusted them, didn't we? --Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,--Liars! --Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't trust them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't trust them because they're humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how we've always treated humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Super...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.69,0:12:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...Afro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,--Franky-san, that's so cool! --Isn't it super?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.23,0:12:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Chopper, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,--Thanks. --Oh boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.11,0:12:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,When I use the Monster Point,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even walk for a couple hours from fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can still treat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.15,0:12:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody looks okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin-chan! I used a daring technique and I'm exhausted too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:13:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me put my head in your lap, too! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,--Put your stupid head somewhere else! --You do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Princes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that they're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hody! --Vander Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Father! We are sorry to make you worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am glad that you are all okay-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.62,0:14:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody! No worries!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't allow them to make trouble again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We can live without fear now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.51,0:14:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe there was such an awful guy so nearby in the Fishman District.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,--C-Captain Hody! --He looks like a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They are back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.36,0:14:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Straw Hat Luffy and Princess Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot stop Luffy-sama's bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Luffy, stay with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama pushed himself so far in order to save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There are hemostatics in my backpack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,--Get it for me, Robin. --Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This makes me worried about how you'll fight from now on, Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-I'll help you move. --We have an odd doctor here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A little bit to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Luffy-sama be all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.37,0:15:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can stop the bleeding but he already lost a lot of blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lacking blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy is the only one with blood type F among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be somebody in the plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there someone with blood type F here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.09,0:16:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can somebody donate blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Nobody?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My blood type is F.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine is F but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, your blood type is F, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! Donating blood to humans is prohibited in this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of law is that?! That's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you! Luffy is dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My blood type is not F but mine's red too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.66,0:16:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes but thank you for offering!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Shirahoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! There are human pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:17:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey please! If nothing is done, Luffy is gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy is gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Take my blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's F.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have as much as you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's against the law...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It is okay-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,K-King-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.52,0:17:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is so wrong with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That old law is also...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...a curse-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let me prepare for the procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.70,0:18:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine now. I can move for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe, it may hurt a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hurt somebody...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.07,0:19:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...or if somebody hurts you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the same red blood will be shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It hardly seems like a path...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...because it's a very thin and narrow tube - but it makes its way through...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.49,0:20:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...the prejudice that makes people fear each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...and blood feuds...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...so very easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a path towards a very real sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,not some empty wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.35,0:21:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama, you came to life again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.86,0:21:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--Luffy! --Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.86,0:21:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.73,0:21:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that you were awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.67,0:21:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.01,0:22:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We are back to zero now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.31,0:22:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.86,0:23:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jinbe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.34,0:23:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Join...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.38,0:23:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...my crew!
Comment: 0,0:23:16.98,0:23:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Missing Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.50,0:23:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.90,0:23:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Secret Revealed! The Truth about the Ancient Weapon!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.01,0:23:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
